authors: Steffen Forkmann, Daniel Mohl, Tomas Petricek, Ryan Riley, Mauricio Scheffer, Phil Trelford
description: FSharpx.Extras implements general functional constructs on top of the F# core library. Its main target is F# but it aims to be compatible with all .NET languages wherever possible.It currently implements:* Several standard monads: State, Reader, Writer, Either, Continuation, Distribution* Validation applicative functor* General functions like flip* Additional functions around collections* Functions to make C# - F# interop easier.
